= "We want to explore whether there may be scope for third sector organisations to develop data coops for community benefit". 

URL = http://www.ourdata.coop/ 

This link seems to be broken since 2018. The last working archived version on waybackmachine on May 2017 :  https://web.archive.org/web/20170519095756/http://www.ourdata.coop/


=Description=

"We want to test whether data coops could combine personal, organisational and public open data and function as asset-locked vehicles so that the sector is better placed to understand the costs/impact associated with different approaches to service delivery; evidence ‘better for less’ or alternative service proposals to commissioners; and influence evidence-based policy-making activities on the basis of robust evidence."

